
Revision history for Net-Async-SMTP

0.002     2014-04-22 03:28:51+01:00 Europe/London
	No new features.

	Dependencies:
	* IO::Async::Resolver::DNS is now required rather than recommended, since
	it changes the behaviour of the core IO::Async::Loop resolver and the alternative
	(doing this at runtime via 'require' instead of 'use') seems potentially risky

0.001     2014-04-20 17:01:48+01:00 Europe/London
	Initial CPAN release

